            <SectionHeader Title="Color Picker Mode">
                <Description>You can set the default mode of the colorpicker by changing <CodeInline>ColorPickerMode</CodeInline>, if you dont want the users to be able to switch mode you can disable the switch with <CodeInline>DisableColorModeSwitch</CodeInline> prop.</Description>
            </SectionHeader>
